<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p><strong>Jumia Cross-Selling Tool Chrome Extension</strong></p>

<p>This Privacy Policy explains how the Cross-Selling Tool Chrome Extension handles user information.</p>

<div class="section">
<h2>1. Information Collection</h2>

<p>
The Cross-Selling Tool does <strong>not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal information</strong>.
</p>

<p>The extension operates entirely within the user's browser and only reads limited product information from the webpage to generate cross-selling suggestions.</p>

</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>2. Data Used by the Extension</h2>

<p>The extension may temporarily read the following information from the active webpage:</p>

<ul>
<li>Product title</li>
<li>Product category information visible on the page</li>
<li>Product page context (Product Display Page)</li>
</ul>

<p>This information is used only to generate item pairing suggestions within the browser session.</p>

<div class="note">
No data is stored, transmitted externally, or linked to any user identity.
</div>

</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>3. No Personal Data Collection</h2>

<p>The extension does not collect or process:</p>

<ul>
<li>Personal information</li>
<li>User account data</li>
<li>Browsing history</li>
<li>Cookies</li>
<li>Authentication information</li>
<li>Payment information</li>
</ul>

<p>All processing occurs locally within the browser.</p>

</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>4. Data Storage</h2>

<p>
The extension does not store user data locally or remotely. No databases, analytics services, or external APIs are used for data collection.
</p>

</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>
The extension does not integrate with third-party tracking services, analytics platforms, or advertising networks.
</p>

</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>6. Security</h2>

<p>
Because the extension does not collect or transmit personal data, there is no exposure of user information to external systems.
</p>

</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>

<p>
This privacy policy may be updated if the extension functionality changes in the future. Any updates will be reflected on this page.
</p>

</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>8. Contact</h2>

<p>
For questions regarding this privacy policy, please contact the extension developer.
</p>

</div>

